Uses of Interface
com.iopipe.plugin.IOpipePluginExecution

  • Packages that use IOpipePluginExecution 
    Package Description
    com.iopipe
    This package contians the classes and interfaces which are used to interact with the IOpipe service.
    com.iopipe.plugin
    This package contains the support for plugins which may be used to add functionality so that the client may utilize more monitoring tools.
    com.iopipe.plugin.profiler
    This package contains the profiler plugin which is used to profile code executions made by user code.
    com.iopipe.plugin.trace
    This contains the trace plugin implementation.
